  "summary": {
    "en": "A 130-piece creative STEM fort kit for indoor building, glow-themed play, and gift-ready learning activities.",
    "zh": "130件创意STEM堡垒拼搭套装，适合室内搭建、夜光主题玩法和礼品化学习活动。"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": [
      "The 130-piece set supports indoor forts, tents, towers, and imaginative structures for children ages 5 and up.",
      "Lightweight PP parts are easy to connect, remove, and rebuild for repeated learning and play.",
      "Glow-themed packaging and structures make the item suitable for gifts, night play, and themed retail programs.",
      "Custom packaging, branding, and accessory combinations can be discussed for OEM/ODM cooperation."
    ],
    "zh": [
      "130件套支持室内堡垒、帐篷、高塔和想象力结构，适合5岁以上儿童。",
      "轻便PP配件易于连接、拆卸和重建，适合反复学习与玩耍。",
      "夜光主题包装和结构适合礼品、夜间玩法和主题零售项目。",
      "可根据OEM/ODM合作沟通包装、品牌和配件组合。"
    ]
  },
